Communications Templates:

1. Internal Notification:

Subject: Important Security Alert - Phishing Incident Detected
 
Dear Team,
We have identified a phishing incident involving [brief description]. Please avoid interacting with
suspicious messages and report concerns to [Contact Information]. Steps are underway to resolve
the situation.
  
2. Client Notification:

Subject: Notice of Phishing Incident

Dear Client,
We recently identified a phishing attack that may impact some of our clients. We recommend that
you reset your password and monitor your accounts closely. We are actively working to secure our
systems.
